txt.en: 'The journey here was far more perilous than I ever expected. I cannot believe we escaped without further incident.'
'Yes... this swamp is naught but bleakness and despair. I hope that we can render some aid ere we depart.'
'My heart fails me in Mirkwood. The shadow of Dol Guldur has crept too far and too deep; I do not think we can set things right again, sister.'
